The part with â€œ&lt;div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;â€ means that there is a block on the webpage. This block corresponds to the one where all the individual articles are listed. There are many blocks on a webpage, so we can give them different names to avoid confusing them. Here, the block is called â€œpart_list_2â€.
