The second element is an â€œ&lt;em&gt;&lt;/em&gt;â€ element (why â€œemâ€ and not â€œspanâ€? â€œemâ€ stands for â€œemphasisâ€, so they look different on the website). Its name is â€œtag c_newsâ€.
The third element is an â€œ&lt;a&gt;&lt;/a&gt;â€ element. This is used to write a text with a link, and the link is specified with â€œhrefâ€. The term â€œtarget=â€_blankâ€â€ means that it opens in a new page when you click on it.








